-I have you to thank for this.
-This is nothing.

41
00:03:13,960 --> 00:03:15,240
Do you think I can go first

42
00:03:15,320 --> 00:03:16,640
in the exam today?

43
00:03:16,920 --> 00:03:18,120
You have plans for the afternoon?

44
00:03:18,200 --> 00:03:20,000
I have an interview at
the TCM Hospital at 4 pm.

45
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:22,680
