get there by 3.30pm.

46
00:03:22,760 --> 00:03:23,880
Why don't you take a taxi?

47
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:26,000
A taxi.

48
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:28,080
I will order it for you.

49
00:03:29,520 --> 00:03:30,640
That's very nice of you.

50
00:03:31,160 --> 00:03:32,560
Let's settle for some instant noodles.

51
00:03:32,640 --> 00:03:34,160
