85
00:04:43,520 --> 00:04:46,280
I'm in the garden on the east side.
You are the on the west side?

86
00:04:46,880 --> 00:04:48,480
Okay. I'll be right over.

87
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:49,840
Okay, thank you.

88
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:51,320
