you could've just admitted it.

90
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:56,080
I would understand.
I'm sure others would too.

91
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:58,400
But you are lying through
your teeth right in front of me.

92
00:04:58,480 --> 00:05:00,840
Hang on. If you hadn't been
wasting my time, I...

93
00:05:00,920 --> 00:05:01,920
The order is cancelled.

94
00:05:03,440 --> 00:05:04,440
Stop right there!

95
00:05:06,880 --> 00:05:08,640
So, you are going to
be unreasonable, huh?

96
00:05:09,800 --> 00:05:10,800
Do you still want it or not?

97
00:05:10,880 --> 00:05:12,280
-No.
-No?

98
00:05:12,600 --> 00:05:13,600
Fine. Take this!

99
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:23,920
Coming!

100
00:05:24,320 --> 00:05:25,360
