101
00:05:32,200 --> 00:05:33,800
(Ren Tian Zhen)

102
00:05:43,200 --> 00:05:44,920
Are you sure this kid is the one?

103
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:46,520
I am positive.

104
00:05:47,520 --> 00:05:49,120
I had the same headache as you

105
