110
00:05:59,880 --> 00:06:01,160
without discrimination?

111
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:02,920
So, how?

112
00:06:04,760 --> 00:06:05,760
Can you

113
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:07,840
turn this kid into

114
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:10,560
the successor of the sect?

115
00:06:14,640 --> 00:06:15,640
Tianquan acu point.

116
00:06:16,040 --> 00:06:17,040
Binao acu point.

117
00:06:18,080 --> 00:06:19,080
Anterior axillary.

118
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:28,160
What did he order?
It smells so good.

119
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:39,920
Tian Zhen, are you okay?

120
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:42,800
Did you fall?

121
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:51,480
I should get going.

122
00:06:52,520 --> 00:06:54,000
(Zhao Li Quan)

123
00:06:54,160 --> 00:06:55,800
Don't be late for your thesis defence.

124
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:03,000
(Jiangzhou University of
Chinese Medicine Affiliated Hospital)

125
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:06,800
It's rejected again?

126
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:09,960
I just don't get it.

127
00:07:10,440 --> 00:07:12,120
Why is it so hard

128
00:07:12,440 --> 00:07:14,720
to get things done these days?

129
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:15,840
Calm down, Shan Dao.

130
00:07:15,960 --> 00:07:17,840
When you encounter a problem,
always remember

131
00:07:18,400 --> 00:07:20,040
to stay neutral and calm.

132
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:22,800
It's been so long.

133
00:07:22,920 --> 00:07:24,440
Even God would lost His patience.

134
00:07:25,120 --> 00:07:26,200
This is my bad.

135
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:28,520
I wanted to hold a succession program me,

136
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:30,120
an apprentice training program me.

137
00:07:30,200 --> 00:07:31,960
I brought this trouble to myself.

138
00:07:35,600 --> 00:07:36,600
Shao Dao,

139
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:38,120
the problem of TCM education

140
00:07:38,240 --> 00:07:39,640
in some parts of our country

141
00:07:39,760 --> 00:07:41,240
is becoming more and more obvious.

142
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:42,720
You see, if we teach

143
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:45,640
our students using
a Western medical mindset,

144
00:07:45,760 --> 00:07:48,600
