Ma Liang, said?

283
00:14:48,160 --> 00:14:50,480
You are a university president.

284
00:14:50,800 --> 00:14:52,600
Managing a school

285
00:14:52,680 --> 00:14:54,480
is already challenging enough.

286
00:14:54,600 --> 00:14:55,520
Why choose

287
00:14:55,600 --> 00:14:57,160
to walk this path?

288
00:14:57,960 --> 00:14:58,880
You see,

289
00:14:58,960 --> 00:14:59,960
I

290
00:15:00,440 --> 00:15:02,920
have spent half of my life teaching.

291
00:15:03,240 --> 00:15:04,320
I have taught

292
00:15:05,240 --> 00:15:06,400
many practising doctors,

293
00:15:07,480 --> 00:15:09,200
but there are still too many patients,

294
00:15:09,280 --> 00:15:11,160
and they will never stop coming.

295
00:15:11,440 --> 00:15:14,720
In fact, we are focusing too much
on the superficial aspects

296
00:15:15,200 --> 00:15:16,840
and neglecting the essence of TCM.

297
00:15:17,440 --> 00:15:18,560
The essence of TCM lies in

298
00:15:19,240 --> 00:15:23,200
the prevention and treatment
of illnesses before they manifest.

299
00:15:23,560 --> 00:15:25,240
The highest level of medical practice
focuses on preventing diseases,

300
00:15:25,360 --> 00:15:26,840
middle-level physicians
treat potential illnesses,

301
00:15:26,920 --> 00:15:29,160
and lower-level physicians
treat existing diseases.

302
00:15:29,600 --> 00:15:31,120
We ourselves are considered
lower-level physicians,

303
00:15:31,200 --> 00:15:32,520
and the students we teach

304
00:15:32,840 --> 00:15:34,080
also fall into that category.

305
00:15:35,080 --> 00:15:36,160
We have not fully demonstrated

306
00:15:36,240 --> 00:15:37,520
the characteristics of TCM.

307
00:15:39,600 --> 00:15:41,240
My biggest dream is to

308
00:15:41,360 --> 00:15:43,000
spread the knowledge of TCM

309
00:15:43,080 --> 00:15:44,880
to every household.

310
00:15:45,440 --> 00:15:46,440
Nip the illness

311
00:15:47,040 --> 00:15:48,080
in the bud.

312
00:15:50,360 --> 00:15:51,360
I was thinking that

313
00:15:51,800 --> 00:15:52,960
I might even

314
00:15:53,080 --> 00:15:54,640
nurture another genius like

315
00:15:55,200 --> 00:15:56,360
Chang Sang or Bian Que,

316
00:15:56,800 --> 00:15:58,840
I would be able to honour
my predecessors then.

317
00:16:00,040 --> 00:16:01,880
That's quite a confident statement.

318
00:16:01,960 --> 00:16:02,960
Good.

319
00:16:03,360 --> 00:16:05,920
He is on his path
to achieve great things,

320
00:16:06,200 --> 00:16:07,280
