323
00:16:12,200 --> 00:16:13,200
Madam,

324
00:16:13,440 --> 00:16:14,560
I've made up my mind.

325
00:16:15,320 --> 00:16:16,600
Spreading the knowledge of TCM

326
00:16:17,160 --> 00:16:19,120
is my responsibility and ideal.

327
00:16:19,960 --> 00:16:21,440
Today, TCM has lost

328
00:16:21,840 --> 00:16:23,040
its ancient methods

329
00:16:23,400 --> 00:16:24,920
of self-preservation.

330
00:16:25,280 --> 00:16:27,440
If it loses the foundation
of self-health,

331
00:16:27,760 --> 00:16:28,840
then TCM has truly reached

332
00:16:28,920 --> 00:16:31,480
a state of forgetting its roots

333
00:16:31,800 --> 00:16:33,600
